"{\"uid\": \"rferl.org-a-kazakhstan-olympic-committee-golovkin-kulibaev-nazarbaev-32837193.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Share  Share  Print  The Kazakh National Olympic Committee said on February 26 that former world boxing champion Gennady Golovkin has replaced ex-President Nursultan Nazarbaev's son-in-law, Timur Kulibaev, as its president.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakh_language\", \"score\": 0.6591804893102867, \"rank\": 0.5170351252328185, \"text\": \"Kazakh\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakh_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakh_language\"}, {\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 58, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999966274169793, \"rank\": 2.7927279183407756e-06, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 113, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gennady_of_Novgorod\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gennady\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gennady_of_Novgorod\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gennady_of_Novgorod\"}, {\"begin\": 156, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nursultan_Nazarbayev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nursultan Nazarbaev\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nursultan_Nazarbayev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nursultan_Nazarbayev\"}, {\"begin\": 190, \"end\": 195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timur\", \"score\": 0.9999925034984654, \"rank\": 7.49652852769025e-06, \"text\": \"Timur\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timur\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Billionaire Kulibaev had led the committee since 2015.\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 224, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billionaire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.669637652926991e-19, \"text\": \"Billionaire\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billionaire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billionaire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nazarbaev, his relatives, and close associates have lost influence in the country following unprecedented anti-government protests in January 2022 that turned deadly after security forces used firearms to disperse demonstrators.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nursultan_Nazarbayev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nazarbaev\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nursultan_Nazarbayev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nursultan_Nazarbayev\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Golovkin, known as \\\"Triple G,\\\" has held multiple middleweight world championships and is a two-time former unified champion.To read the original story by RFE/RL's Kazakh Service, clickhere.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 662, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_Free_Europe/Radio_Liberty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RFE/RL\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_Free_Europe/Radio_Liberty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_Free_Europe/Radio_Liberty\"}, {\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakh_language\", \"score\": 0.6591804893102867, \"rank\": 0.5170351252328185, \"text\": \"Kazakh\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakh_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpe